---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Now">
  <div class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Now</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: March 29, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          This is a <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener">now page</a>.
          It tells you what I'm up to at this point in my life.
        </p>

        <p>Right now, I am</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Making this website. I want it to feel like a creative project that shows you a side of who I am as a person instead of a professional front. Still deliberating what to include.</li>
          <li>Learning about astrophysical radiative processes. Wouldn't necessarily recommend.</li>
          <li>Wrapping up two astro projects — stay tuned...</li>
          <li>Trying to read more, currently reading <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/215020997-bury-our-bones-in-the-midnight-soil" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Bury Our Bones in the Midnight Soil</em></a></li>
          <li>Slowly getting back to running; one day I will conquer the Berkeley hills</li>
          <li>Thinking about my career, figuring out what I actually enjoy doing</li>
          <li>Listening to <a href="https://www.listentofeist.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Multitude</a>, 
          <a href="https://www.dodie.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dodie</a>,
           <a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/4I2BJf80C0skQpp1sQmA0h" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Belle and Sebastian</a>, 
           <a href="https://anginedepoitrine.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Angine de Poitrine</a></li>
        </ul>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .updated {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
